{{Infobox book | name = As She Left It | image = As She Left It.jpg | author = Catriona McPherson | genre = [[Mystery fiction]], [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]], [[Crime (genre)|Crime]] | published = 2013 | publisher = Midnight Ink Books | isbn = 978-0-738-73677-8 | alt = As She Left It | pages = 343 | website = {{URL|http://catrionamcpherson.com/standalones/as-she-left-it|As She Left It}} | awards = [[Anthony Award|Anthony Award for Best Paperback Original]] (2014) }}
'''As She Left It''' is a book written by Catriona McPherson<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=vVzHAe5JpIEC&source=gbs_navlinks_s|title=As She Left It: A Novel|last=McPherson|first=Catriona|date=2013-06-01|publisher=Llewellyn Worldwide|isbn=9780738736778|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://catrionamcpherson.com/standalones/as-she-left-it|title=As She Left It : Stand Alone Novels {{!}} Catriona McPherson|website=catrionamcpherson.com|access-date=2017-03-27}}</ref> and published by Midnight Ink Books<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.midnightinkbooks.com/product.php?ean=9780738736778|title=Midnight Ink - Product Detail - As She Left It|website=www.midnightinkbooks.com|access-date=2017-03-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/978-0-7387-3677-8|title=Fiction Book Review: As She Left It by Catriona McPherson. Midnight Ink (www.midnightinkbooks.com), $14.99 trade paper (360p) ISBN 978-0-7387-3677-8|work=PublishersWeekly.com|access-date=2017-03-27|language=en}}</ref> (an imprint of [[Llewellyn Worldwide]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/as-she-left-it-catriona-mcpherson/1113557697|title=As She Left It|last=Noble|first=Barnes &|website=Barnes & Noble|language=en|access-date=2017-03-27}}</ref>) on 8 June 2013, which later went on to win the [[Anthony Award]] for Best Paperback Original in 2014.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bouchercon.com/anthony-awards/winners-and-nominees/|title=Winners and Nominees|date=2015-08-10|work=Bouchercon|access-date=2017-03-27|language=en}}</ref>
